+# Copilot v2 producer test migration
+
+```text
+historical v1 artifact -> extract_advisory() -> readable historical evidence
+
+active fake Copilot -> four-field first opinion -> active producer
+                    -> copilot_advisory.v2 -> dual-artifact manifest
+```
+
+The two paths are intentionally distinct. No mapping from v1 analysis fields to
+v2 analysis fields is defined.
